  "contradictions": [
    {
      "documentation": "docs/architecture/tech-stack.md, docs/architecture/overview.md and docs/packages/auth.md describe the dashboard authentication as Auth.js v5 + Cognito OIDC and the dashboard persistence layer as direct DynamoDB via AWS SDK v3 + KMS.",
      "implementation": "apps/dashboard/src/middleware.ts and apps/dashboard/src/lib/api/with-auth.ts use Clerk (@clerk/nextjs) at runtime; apps/dashboard/src/lib/api/http-api-client.ts and get-backend-token.ts proxy all data through the CauseFlow Core API (CORE_API_URL); no Dashboard code path runs Auth.js, Cognito, DynamoDB, or KMS at runtime \u2014 only scripts/delete-user.ts and the temporary tenant-provisioning-fallback use DynamoDB directly.",
      "resolution": "Concretely: dashboard auth = Clerk (not Auth.js/Cognito); dashboard data = Core API proxy (not direct DynamoDB); AWS SDK in this repo is limited to the tenant-provisioning-fallback and the user-deletion CLI script."
    },
    {
      "documentation": "docs/architecture/tech-stack.md and apps/website/.env.example (LOOPS_API_KEY) describe a Loops.so email-marketing integration exposed via the website's /api/notify route.",
      "implementation": "apps/website/src/app has no /api directory \u2014 the Loops.so integration has no current consumer in this codebase. Only the CSP connect-src in apps/website/next.config.mjs references https://app.loops.so.",
      "resolution": "Concretely: Loops.so is declared as a planned integration in docs and env templates but no runtime code path consumes it."
    },
    {
      "documentation": "docs/architecture/tech-stack.md names pnpm 10.30.1 as the package manager version.",
      "implementation": "package.json pins packageManager: pnpm@10.33.0.",
      "resolution": "Use pnpm 10.33.0 as the active version; the docs reference 10.30.1 which is stale."
    },
    {
      "documentation": "Older inventory listed apps/dashboard/scripts/setup-stripe.ts and Stripe SDKs in dashboard package.json",
